flowchart TD
    MAIN["MAIN PROGRAM Stream Orchestrator Event loop · coordinates all subroutines"]

    MAIN --> INGEST["Subroutine: Ingest Receive RTMP feed from producer"]
    MAIN --> TRANSCODE["Subroutine: Transcode Convert to multiple bitrate renditions"]
    MAIN --> SEGMENT["Subroutine: Segment Split into HLS chunks · .m3u8 playlist"]
    MAIN --> DISTRIBUTE["Subroutine: Distribute Push segments to CDN edge nodes"]
    MAIN --> MONITOR["Subroutine: Monitor Check latency · viewer count · stream health"]

    INGEST --> |"raw stream"| TRANSCODE
    TRANSCODE --> |"360p · 720p · 1080p"| SEGMENT
    SEGMENT --> |"HLS chunks"| DISTRIBUTE
    MONITOR --> |"health signal"| MAIN

    MAIN --> ARCHIVE["Subroutine: Archive Write completed event to VOD storage"]